missTags/selfRating/correctness were written by reflection and read by nothing.
GET /weaknesses now derives reason/pattern/topic signals from windowed attempts
(plan §5.4; no new table per §2.1.8 'derived from real attempts').
Recommendations gain weakness-repair items at priority 95 (§6.1 slot 3) with
§6.2-style concrete reasons, gated at ≥2 struggles. weak_area_review sessions —
previously identical to quick_practice — now redo recent unrepaired misses and
fill with siblings from the weakest patterns/topics, falling back to the
filtered draw for users with no history.
